messages.content: I'm not really sure what you're getting at with the "hki" but I'll play along! Can you tell me more about what's on your mind today?
Hello there how are u today
Im doin alright, just got back from a pretty long day of work. You know how it is. So, what brings you here today?
Oh my i see , tired right? Me too , well am just passing by and want to know how
I'm glad I'm not the only one feeling a bit drained lately! Yeah, work can be really exhausting sometimes. So, what's new with you? Got any exciting plans or anything?
